      <div class="comment-body markdown-body markdown-format js-comment-body">
          <p>Looking forward to Lechezar's response on this. I really to believe it's that simple, just was confused that it was removed from the repo. Adding that to the decision to go in the direction of integrating with intents, I just didn't want to step on any toes.</p>

<p>Offtopic: I understand what you mean, which i suppose is part of the reason i'm asking this question instead of just throwing my own class together, it would defeat the advantages of an open source codebase if I did. "Preference" might have been the wrong word. I just worry for the environment where a device is set up with an application that needs to scan barcodes. (Pre-installed apk, no playstore credentials to install apps, etc)</p>
